('e391d2fc-b1ad-5ced-a39f-69acb7f9afb4', '2bcb0ca4-f12e-4a0b-a5a2-6dc50a3f705d', 'Scientists are concerned that the rapid loss of habitat will destroy the lives of many ___ in the rainforest.', '科學家擔心棲息地的快速喪失將摧毀熱帶雨林中許多動物的生命。', 'animals', 'machines', 'buildings', 'vehicles', 'anim (生命/靈魂)', 'animal (動物) → 想到 anim (soul/生命)', '2026-07-06 21:21:36', '2026-07-06 21:21:36'),
('30558750-8dcf-5d4a-84e9-47f3ee2bff4c', 'f2c0ea2d-c631-49dd-8fe8-10d3d40c3ef9', 'The fans waited in great ___ for the singer''s first performance on stage.', '粉絲們帶著極大的期待等待著歌手在舞台上的首次表演。', 'anticipation', 'hesitation', 'confidence', 'frustration', 'ante- (在...之前) + cip (拿/取) + -ation (名詞字尾) → 在事情發生前就先取得 → 預期。', '想像在事情發生「之前」(ante) 就先「抓取」(cip) 到了那個感覺，就是「預期/期待」。', '2026-07-06 21:52:31', '2026-07-06 21:52:31'),
('2b6c2bc3-7ea4-5e85-a34f-fb0760ae7ce0', '9e87aeb1-33ac-4530-bb13-b40fb7a0a0a7', 'The movie will start ___ 7:00 PM.', '電影大約在晚上七點開始。', 'around', 'since', 'during', 'before', 'a (在) + round (圓形) → 在圓圈的範圍內。', '想像時間點在一個圓圈範圍內 → 大約。', '2026-07-06 14:49:28', '2026-07-06 14:49:28'),
